        "Detailed analysis of each 10 criteria",
        "Incremental improvement recommendations (low/medium/high cost)",
        "ROI projections and market impact",
        "Before/after visualization concepts",
        "Professional contractor recommendations",
        "Timeline and priority matrix",
        "Local market insights"
      ],
      "technical_requirements": [
        "PDF generation with professional templates",
        "Dynamic content based on AI analysis",
        "Cost estimation database",
        "Market data integration"
      ]
    }
  },
